# Non-code and heavy blobs - keeps Cursor index / @-file search focused on source.
# Tune negations below if you need a path back in context.

# --- Prose & docs ---
*.md
docs/

# --- Data corpora, tag banks, caption dumps ---
# data/ (do not ignore all; ignore heavy subsets below)

# --- Bundled payloads (not source) ---
assets/

# --- Media & model weights ---
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
*.bmp
*.ico
*.svg
*.tif
*.tiff
*.heic
*.avif
*.mp4
*.webm
*.mov
*.mkv
*.wav
*.mp3
*.flac
*.ogg
*.pdf
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
*.safetensors
*.ckpt
*.bin
*.npz
*.npy
*.pkl
*.pickle

# --- Tabular / serialized (not application source) ---
*.csv
*.tsv
*.json

# --- Plain text dumps (keep Python dependency lists) ---
*.txt
!requirements.txt
!requirements-*.txt

# --- Config / manifest formats (not code; re-include essentials) ---
*.toml
!pyproject.toml
!**/Cargo.toml
!native/mojo/pixi.toml
!**/.cargo/config.toml
*.yaml
*.yml
!.github/workflows/**

*.ini
*.cfg
*.properties
.editorconfig
.gitattributes
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
docker-compose*.yaml

# --- Markup / notebooks when present ---
*.html
*.htm
*.ipynb

# --- License / notices (plain text) ---
LICENSE*
LICENCE*
NOTICE*
CHANGELOG*

# --- Secrets & local env ---
.env
.env.*

# --- Tooling trees (not project source) ---
.venv/
venv/
**/node_modules/
**/target/
**/.zig-cache/
**/zig-out/

# --- Large optional trees (match .gitignore intent) ---
external/
enhanced_dit/
pretrained/
results/
# --- Re-include prompt tag CSVs for editing ---
!data/prompt_tags/
!data/prompt_tags/*.csv
# --- Re-include python data modules ---
!data/**/*.py
# --- Heavy data subsets ---
data/danbooru/
data/civitai/
